[SHORT DESC]
Portable plant pot for growing Berries.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Only available in HeartGold and SoulSilver. Allows Berries to be grown without the need for loamy soil which is missing from HeartGold and SoulSilver. Has four pots, each of which can contain one growing Berry Plant. Berry plants may be tended to while in the pots.</p>